lity, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#216<br />\n應該冇加料 UV燈照過安全，番簡水、梳打水可行</span><br />\n<br />\n#252<br />\n綠藻濃縮液，用水開搽落皮膚到捽都可以，唔傷皮膚"},{"pid":"4fa90ce68f8b91158b9bb06a4a38ad0ae31b101b","tid":1570890,"uid":57221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62b155b9de82bbb46da981ff8c78adbb67078a49","tid":1570890,"uid":139282,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T09:48:53.000Z","msg":"求吓大家幫手copy呢段去spread開啊<br />\n<br />\n［化學］如何清洗顏色水劑（含acrylics/PMMA）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1406604\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1406604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. hot sodium carbonate solution</span><br />\n<br />\n-蘇打水，溫度50度或更高，建議自己開，落多小小都唔怕<br />\n（同小蘇打sodium bicarbonate有啲分別，唔知bicarbonate效果係點）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.消毒火酒（酒精）/含消毒火酒成份濕紙巾</span><br />\n<br />\n3<span style=\"color: red;\">.化妝水</span>/卸妝水/洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n可以洗到有acrylics/PMMA嘅顏料<br />\n<br />\n紅字係考慮完availability, effectiveness, usefulness, side-effects嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外衫褲鞋襪可以先噴防水噴霧<br />\n中招就唔好留直接dum咗佢</span><br />\n<br />\n消毒火酒：<br />\n易買 平 可用作消毒 但係多用傷皮膚<br />\n化/卸妝水：<br />\n女仔會有 比較唔傷皮膚 但貴 同埋唔同牌子效果可能會有差異<br />\n<br />\n其他建議：<br />\n#67 威猛先生玻璃劑<br />\n#91 含酒精成分濕紙巾<br />\n#117 大塊顏料可以待乾再成塊搣<br />\n<br />\n#127<br />\n可以搽定凡士林/hand cream<br />\n保持皮膚濕潤方便移除顏料<br />\n<br />\n#145<br />\n唔敢去五金可以去模型舖買Mr Color paint remover/Mr Color tool cleaner，冇就買住水性油天拿水頂住先<br />\n<br />\n#148<br />\n補充使用順序：<br />\n先用水性油天拿水或者75%酒精捽<br />\n好頑固捽唔到嗰啲先用paint remover/tool cleaner<br />\n因為用完呢兩隻，啲顏料會變硝基，用唔返酒精<br />\n最後都唔得先好用洗甲水<br />\n<br />\n#164<br />\n凡士林coating，logon $50 gel removal<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#216<br />\n應該冇加料 UV燈照過安全，番簡水、梳打水可行</span><br />\n<br />\n#252<br />\n綠藻濃縮液，用水開搽落皮膚到捽都可以，唔傷皮膚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T09:58:58.000Z","msg":"lpp"},{"pid":"b77bfbaa448a05a0e3171e17f47a4e0066ac0436","tid":1570890,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:00:12.000Z","msg":"你搞尖沙咀啲人咪重難走"},{"pid":"d0eea01f4ef8d02def17e87bd5b4ba8e7d50b604","tid":1570890,"uid":236368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"678140db6943c7bb7edb686b3cca473c191dc49c","tid":1570890,"uid":7168,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T09:20:12.000Z","msg":"等睇尖沙咀落閘收鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:01:53.000Z","msg":"k11近排咁旺，落閘就好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e9ac25c1edc08b02f58be8a3d97937f8b56476","tid":1570890,"uid":280302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:02:07.000Z","msg":"有冇人落!!!"},{"pid":"5cc2137b0a1b6e9ab3a3650cb1a081c97918c73d","tid":1570890,"uid":8909,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/miJfOiC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmiJfOiC.gif&h=d47bb762&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebd4d8e55d14649e0d55fe056618a9c7012cad4d","tid":1570890,"uid":260351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T10:09:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff3603336f7cfc1f4352c3e7b247e1b